# Placeholder Podfile. The real Podfile is auto-generated by `npx cap add ios`
# (or by `pod init` after the .xcodeproj exists). On commit, only the
# source-controlled hand-written files are tracked; the auto-generated
# Podfile.lock / Pods/ tree is in .gitignore.
